Tim McInnerny https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tim_McInnerny 0 Tim McInnerny ( MAK-i-NUR-nee; born 18 September 1956) is an English actor. He is known for his many roles on television and stage. Early in his career he featured as Lord Percy Percy and Captain Darling in the Blackadder series. Tim_McInnerny ( MAK-i-NUR-nee ; born_18_September_1956 ) is an_English_actor .
